text: Tracy Rude (born September 25, 1968) is an American rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1968 births Category:Living people Category:American female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of the United States Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Appleton, Wisconsin
